snippet.title: Monkey Toes Studio
snippet.description:
Monkey Toes Studio is a cause front, collaboration center, purpose driven Theories of Everything Studio founded by published author, tv director, Annie Award nominated voice actor and Emmy Award® nominated actor Greg Ellis.

Greg has acted in Oscar winning movies, directed Hollywood super-stars, produced and written television shows and commercials, performed on the West End stage, voiced cartoon characters for movies, tv series, cartoons, over 100 video games and toys, and published two books.

His film credits include Pirates of the Caribbean 1, 3 & 4, Titanic, Star Trek, Mr. & Mrs. Smith, and Beowulf. As a TV actor he held recurring roles in 24, The X-Files, CSI, Dexter, NCIS, Hawaii Five-O, and many more.
